# Rust
/target/
**/*.rs.bk

# Cargo.lock IS tracked: this crate ships a binary (`cargo install promptguard`
# --locked` reads it) and a library, and a tracked lockfile gives `cargo audit`
# deterministic input across local + CI runs.

